there were legends in the west.

00:15.450 --> 00:16.929
Law men and outlaws alike.

00:19.019 --> 00:22.022
Some legends, some stories,
were better left untold.

00:25.590 --> 00:28.376
But sometimes, the past has
a way of finding the light.

