00:36.297 --> 00:37.950
You're gonna get
yourself killed.

00:53.836 --> 00:57.013
- Whatever happens,
don't come outside.

01:42.319 --> 01:43.755
- Hello Colt.

01:43.929 --> 01:45.366
- I see you got my invitation.

01:46.845 --> 01:48.064
- Oh I got it all right.

01:51.198 --> 01:53.635
