01:57.552 --> 01:58.727
- You got my condolences.

02:05.081 --> 02:06.474
- So now what?

02:06.648 --> 02:08.128
- I'm tired of huntin' vermin.

02:10.391 --> 02:12.044
It's time to end this,

02:12.219 --> 02:14.395
right here, right now.

02:18.573 --> 02:20.270
- You hear that boys?

02:20.444 --> 02:23.882
