pretty harsh words.

02:32.195 --> 02:33.544
I hope you can back 'em up.

02:37.200 --> 02:38.810
- Only one way to find out.

02:41.639 --> 02:42.640
- That's enough.

02:44.164 --> 02:47.036
Colt I warned you not to
bring this fight here boy.

02:47.210 --> 02:48.951
- Sheriff.

02:49.125 --> 02:51.910
With all respect, you better
stay the hell out of this one.

02:54.261 --> 02:56.176
- I don't think so, son.

02:58.090 --> 02:59.918
