judge come Monday morning.

03:16.631 --> 03:19.329
- I never argue with
a man of the law.

03:20.461 --> 03:25.335
Well, I guess we
better surrender, boys.

03:31.254 --> 03:33.517
- Sheriff, you need to
get your ass inside now.

03:38.000 --> 03:40.220
- You brought this
upon yourself.

03:45.834 --> 03:46.791
- What?

03:50.447 --> 03:55.322
Get on at 'em boys.

04:05.332 --> 04:06.158
- Willie!

04:46.198 --> 04:48.200
- Are you scared, slick?

04:49.811 --> 04:50.899
'Cause you should be!

05:03.868 --> 05:08.090
- Remember this?

05:08.264 --> 05:10.440
You should, because
it's gonna send you back

05:10.614 --> 05:12.573
where you belong.

06:13.460 --> 06:14.286
You.

06:15.984 --> 06:17.464
I did everything you asked.

06:18.508 --> 06:19.553
It's finished!

06:21.337 --> 06:22.382
Now end this.

09:06.328 --> 09:07.982
- Uh, good mornin' sunshine.

09:11.028 --> 09:11.812
- Morning.

09:17.513 --> 09:19.167
Some storm we had
last night, huh?

09:21.169 --> 09:22.257
- Yeah, it sure was.

09:26.217 --> 09:28.263
Forget we had dinner
plans here last night?

09:28.437 --> 09:30.004
- Sorry.

09:30.178 --> 09:31.309
It turned out to be a late
night at the hospital,

09:31.483 --> 09:32.963
you know, with
the storm and all.

09:33.137 --> 09:34.008
- Mhm.

09:35.183 --> 09:37.489
