09:52.592 --> 09:53.854
- Karen, I'm not
accusing you of anything.

09:54.028 --> 09:55.551
I'm saying your shift
ended at five am

09:55.725 --> 09:57.248
and it's 7:30.

09:57.422 --> 09:59.076
- Well he's a cop, chief.
- Oh come on, come on.

09:59.250 --> 10:00.338
- I'm going to bed.

10:04.516 --> 10:05.822
I don't want Emily
to know that we're

10:05.996 --> 10:08.695
having problems, so, can
we just pretend to get

10:08.869 --> 10:10.479
along while she's here, please?

10:11.349 --> 10:12.829
- Sure.

10:13.003 --> 10:13.787
- Thanks.

10:21.838 --> 10:22.622
- Hardy.

10:26.060 --> 10:27.235
Whoa, whoa, whoa, slow down.

10:27.409 --> 10:29.367
Meg, Meg say that again.

10:32.501 --> 10:33.371
I'll be right there.

11:07.884 --> 11:09.059
- Please.

11:09.233 --> 11:10.060
Help me.

11:16.763 --> 11:17.633
- Mornin' Terry.

11:17.807 --> 11:18.721
- Sheriff.

11:18.895 --> 11:19.896
