11:26.729 --> 11:29.471
- The day I started to
resent this miserable job.

11:29.645 --> 11:31.516
- I'm sure we could
rectify that for ya.

11:31.691 --> 11:33.344
- Keep trying, Dwayne.

11:33.518 --> 11:35.085
Got your head so far
up the mayor's ass,

11:35.259 --> 11:36.826
