out here for years.

13:02.869 --> 13:05.001
- What would cause all that?

13:05.175 --> 13:07.699
- It depends on the
answer you're looking for.

13:07.874 --> 13:09.527
- How is that?

13:09.701 --> 13:11.573
- Well it's a viscous
attack, sheriff.

13:12.443 --> 13:13.793
- An animal?

13:13.967 --> 13:15.577
- On any other given
day I would say yes.

13:16.708 --> 13:17.797
- What does that mean?

13:19.276 --> 13:21.975
