13:36.250 --> 13:37.338
- My thoughts exactly.

13:38.295 --> 13:39.079
- Thank you doc.

13:42.560 --> 13:43.344
Sandra.

13:44.780 --> 13:46.347
- I must've dozed off, Ethan.

13:46.521 --> 13:48.349
I mean, I didn't even know
that they were even gone

13:48.523 --> 13:50.220
until Terry called.

13:50.394 --> 13:52.179
I mean between
working at the dinner,

13:52.353 --> 13:55.225
watching the kids,
I'm really sorry.

13:55.399 --> 13:56.966
- It's not your fault,
don't worry about it.

13:57.140 --> 13:58.402
Can I talk to that
little one there?

13:58.576 --> 13:59.926
- It's okay darling,
he's the sheriff.

14:01.971 --> 14:04.539
- Come down here sweetheart,
let me ask you a question.

14:05.757 --> 14:07.629
Can you uh, can you
remember what you saw?

14:09.718 --> 14:10.893
- They were monsters.

14:11.067 --> 14:12.460
-  Monsters?

14:12.634 --> 14:13.983
- They weren't monsters.

14:14.157 --> 14:16.333
- No that's okay, that's okay.

14:16.507 --> 14:17.987
Monsters.

14:18.161 --> 14:19.293
Well what kind of
monsters were they?

14:19.467 --> 14:20.860
Can you tell me?

14:21.034 --> 14:23.775
- They had big teeth
and long, sharp claws.

14:23.950 --> 14:25.952
- They were werewolves, retard.

14:26.126 --> 14:26.909
- Okay.

14:28.128 --> 14:28.911
Werewolves.

14:31.435 --> 14:32.828
I think we got
about all we need.

14:33.002 --> 14:34.569
You get 'em home, I'll
contact the parents

14:34.743 --> 14:35.657
to come home early.

14:36.876 --> 14:37.833
If there's anything
else, we'll call ya.

14:38.007 --> 14:39.313
- I appreciate it sheriff.

14:39.487 --> 14:40.183
- Sure.

14:40.357 --> 14:41.141
Thank you dear.

14:42.577 --> 14:43.491
- All right Sandra.

14:43.665 --> 14:45.188
Thanks kids.
- Come on kids.

