so many frat parties

18:41.816 --> 18:43.078
and jello shots.

18:43.252 --> 18:44.819
- I can imagine.

18:44.993 --> 18:47.126
Oh, it's really good to see you.

18:47.300 --> 18:48.736
I missed you.
- I missed you, too.

18:48.910 --> 18:51.869
You know what,
speaking of shots,

18:52.043 --> 18:53.741
I could really use
one before I face

18:53.915 --> 18:55.438
my pill popping mother.

18:55.612 --> 18:57.048
- Oh um, you know what?

18:57.223 --> 18:59.094
Let's actually, I was
gonna go to The Nest.

18:59.268 --> 19:00.878
Let's just meet there
in a few minutes.

19:01.052 --> 19:03.316
- But shots are free here.

19:03.490 --> 19:04.578
Why don't we--

19:04.752 --> 19:05.666
- Um.

19:06.884 --> 19:08.712
I just wanna get out
of the house, you know?

19:08.886 --> 19:10.714
