I'm not nervous.

19:19.201 --> 19:20.811
- You have a guy in
there, don't you?

19:20.985 --> 19:23.205
- It's not like that.
- You slut.

19:23.379 --> 19:24.728
Why didn't you just say so?
- Shut up.

19:24.902 --> 19:25.860
- Okay.

19:26.034 --> 19:27.775
Okay.

19:27.949 --> 19:31.648
You just go back to doing
whatever it is you were doing,

19:31.822 --> 19:33.955
or whoever you were doing.
- There is no--

19:34.129 --> 19:37.611
- And I will go say hello
to my soul crushing parents.

19:42.311 --> 19:44.313
- Hey, don't say anything.

20:27.138 --> 20:28.009
- Where am I?

20:29.489 --> 20:30.751
Where are my clothes?

20:30.925 --> 20:33.841
- It's okay, I have
your things right here.

20:34.015 --> 20:35.886
What I could salvage, anyway.

20:36.060 --> 20:37.192
- My necklace.

20:39.673 --> 20:40.500
- It's right here.

20:46.332 --> 20:47.202
Are you all right?

20:51.685 --> 20:52.773
- The year is...

21:01.956 --> 21:03.174
- They belonged to my husband.

21:03.349 --> 21:04.219
They should fit.

21:09.877 --> 21:11.357
- Good.

21:11.531 --> 21:13.402
I'm gonna need steel, and iron.

21:31.377 --> 21:32.726
Oh, these'll do.

21:37.078 --> 21:38.819
- What do you
think you're doin'?

21:43.563 --> 21:44.999
- You got silver bullets?

21:45.173 --> 21:46.957
- Yeah, actually, I do.

21:47.131 --> 21:48.655
Why, are you huntin' werewolves?

21:50.874 --> 21:52.093
- How far to Canyon Creek?

21:53.312 --> 21:54.530
- Canyon Creek?

21:54.704 --> 21:55.575
Canyon Creek doesn't
exist anymore.

21:55.749 --> 21:56.750
It's Temple Wells now.

21:56.924 --> 21:58.708
- How far?

21:58.882 --> 21:59.927
- 15 minutes.

22:00.754 --> 22:01.537
- Good.

22:04.410 --> 22:05.324
I'll need a horse.

22:12.461 --> 22:13.897
There used to be
stories about the future

22:14.071 --> 22:16.073
having machines just like this.

22:16.247 --> 22:18.380
These horseless carriages.

22:19.555 --> 22:21.122
What do you call it?

22:21.296 --> 22:23.124
- Most people would just
call this a piece of junk.

22:25.561 --> 22:28.085
Have you really never
driven a truck before?

22:28.259 --> 22:30.697
- I've never seen
a truck before.

22:32.481 --> 22:33.874
It must seem strange to you.

22:35.005 --> 22:37.617
- Oh no, nothin'
about you is strange.

22:38.574 --> 22:40.315
So where exactly
am I taking you?

22:42.143 --> 22:43.231
- Take me to a saloon.

22:44.406 --> 22:45.364
- A saloon?

22:46.539 --> 22:47.540
Like a bar?

22:48.454 --> 22:49.716
Why do you wanna go there?

22:50.978 --> 22:52.501
- Well how else do
you get information?

22:53.676 --> 22:55.112
- I don't know, the internet?

22:56.113 --> 22:57.245
- Inter-what?

22:59.682 --> 23:01.336
- All right.

23:01.510 --> 23:04.165
Listen dude, you and I are
gonna make a deal right now.

23:04.339 --> 23:06.385
I'm gonna take you to
the saloon so you can

23:06.559 --> 23:10.693
get your information
and then this is done.

23:10.867 --> 23:12.782
And we're just gonna
go our separate ways.

23:12.956 --> 23:14.088
Deal?

23:14.262 --> 23:15.176
- You have my word.

23:16.569 --> 23:17.396
- All right then.

23:18.527 --> 23:19.876
Now I'm gonna start this engine

23:20.050 --> 23:22.879
