facility or somethin'?

23:43.596 --> 23:44.335
- What?

23:44.510 --> 23:45.336
No.

23:46.773 --> 23:51.125
I come from a place,
well, far away from here.

23:51.299 --> 23:52.213
- Okay.

23:54.345 --> 23:55.390
Well you got a name?

23:56.304 --> 23:57.914
- James Franklin Colt, Jr.

