24:04.704 --> 24:06.314
Did you escape from a hospital?

24:07.402 --> 24:08.447
Do you have issues?

24:09.752 --> 24:11.145
- How are we able
to move this fast?

24:12.842 --> 24:14.583
- Well, the pedal on
the left makes us stop,

24:14.757 --> 24:16.672
and the pedal on the
right makes us go.

24:17.847 --> 24:19.675
Consider that your
first driving lesson.

24:21.547 --> 24:22.548
- Looks easy enough.

24:26.160 --> 24:28.467
Don't worry, I'm no hard case.

24:28.641 --> 24:29.555
I mean you no harm.

24:33.254 --> 24:34.516
- Well that's good to know.

24:37.867 --> 24:41.305
You know, Temple Wells
isn't much to see anymore.

24:41.480 --> 24:43.873
Used to be a mining
town back in the 1800s.

24:45.440 --> 24:46.267
- I know.

25:17.472 --> 25:19.256
- Woo hoo hoo!

25:19.430 --> 25:20.780
Yeah!

25:20.954 --> 25:22.303
Thing kicks like an ex-wife.

25:24.218 --> 25:25.262
- Always a pleasure, Mr. Mayor.

25:25.436 --> 25:26.568
- Yeah it is.

