25:41.757 --> 25:43.846
You look like a man that's
got somethin' on his mind.

25:44.020 --> 25:47.023
So why don't you say what
you came out here to say?

25:49.852 --> 25:51.332
Son of a bitch.

25:51.506 --> 25:53.290
- No see, you're pullin' it.

25:53.464 --> 25:54.161
You gotta squeeze it.

25:54.335 --> 25:55.423
- Eh.

25:55.597 --> 25:56.859
I think it's just the gun.

25:58.121 --> 25:59.819
- I did come out here
to tell you somethin'.

25:59.993 --> 26:00.863
Somethin' serious.

26:03.562 --> 26:04.954
- Well I figure serious
best be rinsed down

26:05.128 --> 26:06.652
with a cocktail, don't you?

26:07.957 --> 26:09.437
Let's move inside.

26:12.875 --> 26:14.050
Well.

26:14.224 --> 26:15.835
I'm not under arrest am I?

26:16.009 --> 26:17.532
- Uh no.

26:17.706 --> 26:18.794
- Well.

26:18.968 --> 26:20.100
Then I'm all ears.

26:20.274 --> 26:21.275
What do you got?

26:21.449 --> 26:22.537
- Well you know Burt Thompson.

26:24.408 --> 26:25.496
Well Burt's dead.

26:25.671 --> 26:27.847
- Oh shit.

26:28.021 --> 26:29.370
- You think that's funny?

26:29.544 --> 26:31.764
- Jesus Christ, Ethan,
look at your face.

26:33.026 --> 26:34.941
You'd think the Marines
had landed or some shit.

26:35.115 --> 26:36.420
He's the town drunk.

26:36.595 --> 26:37.813
I'm surprised he
lasted that long,

26:37.987 --> 26:40.163
been chuggin' turpentine
his whole damn life.

26:40.337 --> 26:41.469
- He was murdered, Bob.

26:43.036 --> 26:45.516
I mean, I think
that's odd, don't you?

26:45.691 --> 26:48.650
That'd be the first homicide
in this little town in,

26:49.695 --> 26:52.436
well ever, as far as I can tell.

26:53.699 --> 26:54.787
- So how'd that happen now?

26:55.657 --> 26:57.224
- I don't know.

26:57.398 --> 26:59.139
Body was pretty torn up.

26:59.313 --> 27:01.228
- How do you even know
it's a homicide then?

27:03.534 --> 27:04.361
- A hunch.

27:05.711 --> 27:07.451
- A hunch?
- Yeah.

27:07.626 --> 27:08.670
- You're crazy.

27:08.844 --> 27:09.889
You gonna hang
your hat on a hunch?

27:10.063 --> 27:10.803
- You'd be surprised.

27:10.977 --> 27:12.718
Cops do it all the time.

27:12.892 --> 27:13.806
You forget about that?

27:13.980 --> 27:15.372
- I don't forget about anything.

27:15.546 --> 27:16.547
- Look I just stopped
by here to tell you

27:16.722 --> 27:18.332
Burt Thompson's dead.

27:18.506 --> 27:20.639
Figured you oughta know,
you being the mayor and all.

27:21.727 --> 27:24.251
- What happened to us, huh?

27:24.425 --> 27:26.079
We used to be
partners, you know.

27:27.471 --> 27:29.299
The two of us, we've
seen more shit than

27:29.473 --> 27:32.259
any two humans are supposed
to see in a goddamn life time.

27:33.521 --> 27:35.349
We used to trust each
other with our lives.

27:35.523 --> 27:36.698
- Yes, sir, we did.

27:39.440 --> 27:40.659
That went right out
the window the day

27:40.833 --> 27:42.356
you started sleepin'
with my wife.

27:54.411 --> 27:55.978
- What the fuck
did you just say?

27:56.152 --> 27:56.936
- You heard me.

27:58.981 --> 28:00.287
You've been carrying
a torch for Karen

28:00.461 --> 28:01.941
since the day you met her.

28:02.115 --> 28:03.943
You know it and I know it.

28:05.118 --> 28:07.990
- Now see Ethan, shit like that.

28:08.164 --> 28:10.906
That's how I know you
lost your goddamn mind.

28:11.080 --> 28:12.603
- She started working
nights all of a sudden,

28:12.778 --> 28:14.649
comin' in early in the morning,
can't look me in the eye.

28:14.823 --> 28:16.782
I don't need to be a cop
to see what's going on.

28:16.956 --> 28:18.609
- Ethan, Ethan, Ethan--

28:18.784 --> 28:21.134
- I'd appreciate it if you
started calling me sheriff.

28:22.091 --> 28:23.266
- Yeah.

28:23.440 --> 28:24.790
- I thank you for the drink.

28:54.471 --> 28:55.472
- Do you mind?

28:55.646 --> 28:56.996
- Sure.

28:57.170 --> 28:58.127
Why the hell not?

28:59.433 --> 29:00.782
- I never got your name.

29:00.956 --> 29:01.740
- It's Lucy.

29:03.393 --> 29:05.831
- Well Lucy, I'm in your debt.

29:07.484 --> 29:08.311
- Wait.

29:09.617 --> 29:10.444
Shit.

29:12.141 --> 29:13.839
You can't go anywhere
without money.

29:17.930 --> 29:18.974
- I'll see you around.

