29:43.085 --> 29:44.565
- What can I get you sweetie?

29:46.262 --> 29:47.046
- Whiskey.

29:48.395 --> 29:49.309
- Particular brand?

29:50.266 --> 29:51.790
- Uh, any kind will do.

29:52.878 --> 29:53.704
- Okay.

29:54.618 --> 29:55.445
On the rocks?

29:56.882 --> 29:58.013
Ice?

29:58.187 --> 29:59.188
- Uh.

29:59.362 --> 30:00.233
Sure.

30:00.407 --> 30:01.234
Why not?

30:06.108 --> 30:08.763
How many bits will this cost me?

30:12.158 --> 30:14.769
