30:14.943 --> 30:18.251
âª After something wrong âª

30:19.252 --> 30:20.557
- You must be new in town.

30:22.472 --> 30:23.212
- Not exactly.

30:24.605 --> 30:26.868
I used to live here
a long time ago.

30:27.042 --> 30:28.827
I'm lookin' for a friend.

30:29.001 --> 30:30.263
- Oh yeah?

30:30.437 --> 30:32.004
Well I know almost everybody.

30:32.178 --> 30:33.092
Who you lookin' for?

30:33.266 --> 30:34.267
- His name's William Price.

30:35.703 --> 30:36.878
- Yeah.

30:37.052 --> 30:38.010
The famous outlaw.

30:38.924 --> 30:39.925
- Famous, you say?

30:40.099 --> 30:41.709
- William Price.

30:41.883 --> 30:44.103
Yeah, he's practically
legendary around these parts.

30:45.539 --> 30:47.715
Murderous outlaw, died
right in the middle of town.

30:48.759 --> 30:50.239
During the Civil War, they say.

30:52.111 --> 30:54.287
- How did he die, exactly?

30:54.461 --> 30:55.288
- Anybody's guess.

30:57.986 --> 31:00.510
- You noticed anything
strange going on in town?

31:00.684 --> 31:02.034
Anything out of the ordinary?

31:04.732 --> 31:07.648
- Man, you're either crazy,

31:09.041 --> 31:09.955
or a cop,

31:11.043 --> 31:12.479
or a reporter.

31:12.653 --> 31:14.220
In which case the
best thing you can do

31:14.394 --> 31:16.309
is finish your drink, and
go talk to the sheriff.

31:17.745 --> 31:18.877
Ask for Ethan Hardy.

31:21.836 --> 31:23.055
